    "The most efficient and long-lasting interventions are MFI.",
    "AI/ML-based assisting tools interventions could be promising for enhancing the appropriate of testing in the future.",
    "Collaboration between clinicians and laboratory staff is key to improve rational laboratory utilization.",
    "Reduction of overuse is overrepresented in the literature in comparison to improvement of underuse.",
    "Moreover, overall methodological quality is poor and study designs lack standardization."
